<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Color Change Squares</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid black;
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 10px #022f60;
            padding: 5vh 5vw;
        }

        .input-section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        #colorInput {
            padding: 8px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            width: 150px;
        }

        #boxSelect {
            padding: 8px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        button{
            padding: 10px 16px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor:pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #022f60;
        }

        .squares {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .row {
            display: flex;
        }

        .square {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #333;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="input-section">
            <input type="text" id="colorInput" placeholder="Enter color name">
            <select id="boxSelect">
                <option value="1">Box 1</option>
                <option value="2">Box 2</option>
                <option value="3">Box 3</option>
                <option value="4">Box 4</option>
                <option value="5">Box 5</option>
                <option value="6">Box 6</option>
                <option value="7">Box 7</option>
                <option value="8">Box 8</option>
            </select>
            <button onclick="changeColor()">Submit</button>
        </div>
        <div class="squares">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="square" id="square1"></div>
                <div class="square" id="square2"></div>
                <div class="square" id="square3"></div>
                <div class="square" id="square4"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="square" id="square5"></div>
                <div class="square" id="square6"></div>
                <div class="square" id="square7"></div>
                <div class="square" id="square8"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        function changeColor() {
            const color = document.getElementById('colorInput').value;
            const selectedBox = document.getElementById('boxSelect').value;

            const squareId = 'square' + selectedBox;
            const square = document.getElementById(squareId);

            if (square) {
                square.style.backgroundColor = color;
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Calculator</title>
</head>
<body>
    <input type="number" id="num1" oninput="calculate()">
    <input type="number" id="num2" oninput="calculate()"> 
    <select id="operation" onchange="calculate()">
        <option value="none">None</option>
        <option value="+">Add</option>
        <option value="-">Subtract</option>
        <option value="*">Multiply</option>
        <option value="/">Divide</option>
    </select>

    <script>
        function calculate() {
            let num1 = document.getElementById('num1').value;
            let num2 = document.getElementById('num2').value;
            let operation = document.getElementById('operation').value;
            if(operation=="none"){

            }
            else{

                let expression = `${num1} ${operation} ${num2}`;
                let result = eval(expression);
                console.log(result);
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>

9.textarea



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width='device-width', initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
      .text
        {height: 200px;
            width: 600px;
            border: 2px solid black;
          } 
      *:hover{
        border-color:red;
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body id="bo">
    <textarea name="" id="text" rows="10" cols="30"></textarea>
    <h1>Css Properties</h1>
    <input type="text" id="color" placeholder="color">
    <input type="text" id="bgcolor" placeholder="background-color">
    <input type="number" id="size" placeholder="fontsize"><br><br>
    <div class="text" id="text1"></div>
    <h3 id="length">Total Letters: <span id="letterCount">0</span></h3>
    
    <script>
           document.getElementById("text").oninput=function(){
            let text=document.getElementById("text").value;
            console.log(text)
            document.getElementById("text1").innerHTML=`<h1>${text}</h1>`;
            let totalLetters = text.length;
            document.getElementById("letterCount").textContent = totalLetters;

        }

        document.getElementById("color").oninput = function() {
          let color = document.getElementById("color").value;
          document.getElementById("text1").style.color = color;
      }

      document.getElementById("bgcolor").oninput = function() {
          let bgcolor = document.getElementById("bgcolor").value;
          document.getElementById("text1").style.backgroundColor = bgcolor;
      }

      document.getElementById("size").oninput = function() {
          let size = document.getElementById("size").value + "px";
          document.getElementById("text1").style.fontSize = size;
      }

    </script>
</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body{
            background-image: url("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQYSn9eqz0M6wJKA9HIEKGb4oKPN3wLjDhBEeE0QMk8yD00CPHpVxiIYxbCo0beJ2W99Cw&usqp=CAU");
        }
    *{
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin-left: 20px;

    }
    .container
    {
        width: 800px;
        background-color: wheat;
        margin-top: 40px;
    }
    button{
        margin:10px;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>My Todo List:</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <input type="text">
        <button>Submit</button>
    </div>
    <script>
        document.querySelector("button").onclick=function()
        {
            let val = document.querySelector("input").value;
            document.querySelector("input").value='';
            document.querySelector("input").focus();
            let h = document.createElement("li");
            let b=document.createElement("button")
            let c=document.createElement("button")
            h.innerHTML=val;
            c.innerHTML="Complete Button"
            b.innerHTML="Delete Button"
            document.querySelector(".container").append(h);
            document.querySelector(".container").append(c);
            document.querySelector(".container").append(b);
            c.onclick = function() {
                h.style.textDecoration = "line-through";
            };
            b.onclick = function() {
                h.remove();
                c.remove();
                b.remove();
            };
        };
    </script>
</body>
</html>
